<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.4.1">
<l>maṇṇai yiruntu tuḻāvi vāmaṉaṉ maṇṇi teṉṉum</l>
<l>viṇṇait toḻutavaṉ mēvu vaikunta meṉṟu kaikāṭṭuṅ</l>
<l>kaṇṇai yuṇīrmalka niṉṟu kaṭalvaṇṇa ṉeṉṉu maṉṉēyeṉ</l>
<l>peṇṇaip perumayal ceytāṟ keṉceykēṉ peyvaḷai yīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sitting [and] stirring the earth she says “this [is] Vāmaṉaṉ’s earth”,</l>
<l>worshipping the sky she gesticulates, saying “Vaikuntam, where he dwells”,</l>
<l>standing while water rises in [her] eyes she says “he with ocean colour”, alas.</l>
<l>To him, who caused the great confusion of my girl, what will I do,</l>
	<l>you with bangles to wear?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
